  ("881A6D64-88EF-437A-9EC8-59A8707B4FBD","https://www.nps.gov/articles/snowoff.htm","Snowoff Date Trends","Read the abstract and get the link to an article published in Remote Sensing that looks at long-term trends of snow-off dates in Alaska: Pan, C. G., P. B. Kirchner, J. S. Kimball, and J. Du. 2020. A long-term passive microwave snowoff record for the Alaska region 1988-2016. Remote Sensing 12(1):153."),
