  ("92A65690-8A00-4B5D-BE16-B7890A86764F","https://www.nps.gov/articles/000/the-homes-of-the-garfield-children-eastlawn.htm","The Homes of the Garfield Children: Eastlawn","Eastlawn was home to Harry Garfield, son of the President and his wife, and his family. The home was part of the country estate that First Lady Garfield planned. Learn more about the home here!"),
