  ("3554AD8F-436D-4F14-96DA-F5FEEAD53C15","https://www.nps.gov/articles/unusually-long-2019-snowy-plover-breeding-season-ends-on-a-high-note.htm","Unusually Long 2019 Snowy Plover Breeding Season Ends on a High Note","The western snowy plover breeding season in Point Reyes National Seashore officially ended on September 11th this year, with the last plover chick fledging on Limantour Beach. Breeding activity persisted unusually late this year, with a couple active nests not hatching until mid August (and subsequently, chicks not fledging until early to mid September). Plovers successfully fledged 15 hatchlings despite a decline in breeding individuals and low nest success."),
  ("8217FB00-07F4-4270-8AB7-0C9F677AB811","https://www.nps.gov/articles/getaway-thko.htm","National Park Getaway: Thaddeus Kościuszko National Memorial","Known as the smallest National Park unit, the Thaddeus Kosciuszko National Memorial is a place to visit where wounded Polish freedom fighter Thaddeus Kosciuszko lived and hear how this brilliant military engineer designed successful fortifications during the American Revolution."),
  ("177A1C05-0EAA-47CA-877E-732411580A04","https://www.nps.gov/articles/gtgtripplan.htm","Trip Plan","You've put a lot of thought into planning for your trip. Have you prepared a trip plan that you can leave with a family or friend who is not going on your trip incase an emergency arises and you don't arrive back when expected? Learn more about what to include in your trip plan."),
