  ("3B98E9D4-7D9E-4D23-9432-F4970DAB2E7A","https://www.nps.gov/articles/protecting-cliff-dwellings-from-wildfire.htm","Protecting Cliff Dwellings from Wildfire","In the summer of 2019, the impending wild Woodbury Fire in the nearby Superstition Wilderness threatened the preserved wood found in these ancient structures. Protecting these cliff dwellings from the fire was a major priority for Tonto National Monument. The Integrated Resources staff decided to cover the cliff dwellings in a fire resistant aluminized structure wrap to shield the prehistoric wood, and preserve the dwellings as a whole."),
  ("56DEB89F-0251-4683-A48A-5480283A1E56","https://www.nps.gov/articles/congratulations-welcome-to-our-conway-science-fellows.htm","Congratulations & Welcome to our National Park Foundation Science Fellows!","We are excited to announce the three fellowship teams selected for the Conway Science Fellowship, which is funded through the support of Karen Swett Conway, National Park Foundation Board of Directors, and her husband Brian Conway. The Conway Science Fellowship is an opportunity for postdoc fellows to conduct research that can help inform management actions of the National Park Service."),
